{"tid":102452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"受川普行政命令波及 有華人入境時綠卡被沒收!?","createTime":"2017-01-31T15:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T03:20:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b914d0a97d77940f6e15c857cac4d7979d4eeac","tid":102452,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:46:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>因川普行政令拖累？ 華人綠卡遭沒收</strong><br />\n<br />\n因要回大陸打點生意 無奈選擇放棄綠卡 以後或要靠商務簽證進出美國<br />\n<br />\n【<strong>大紀元</strong>2017年01月31日訊】<br />\n<br />\n（<strong>大紀元</strong>記者蔡溶紐約報導）川普總統上週六（28日）剛簽署行政命令，暫停接收難民120天，以及限制七個穆斯林國家的公民入境。當天，除了第一波中東人進入美國時遭到盤問，也有持綠卡的華人，<strong>因海外停留時間過長</strong>，<span style=\"color: red;\">在返回美國時，被海關移民官員收走綠卡。</span><br />\n<br />\n「早上9點多我剛上班，就接到一名顧客的電話，他的綠卡被海關扣留了。」紐約永達旅行社經理譚達榮說，這名張姓顧客（化名）上週五從廣州飛抵溫哥華，在溫哥華逗留一天後，上週六準備從溫哥華搭車到西雅圖，入關時被美國海關攔下，「移民官說他持10年綠卡，在美國逗留時間卻不到3個月」。<br />\n<br />\n「<strong>移民官認為他無意在美國居住，要收回他的綠卡</strong>，讓他自動放棄綠卡或進入遞解程序，二選一」，譚達榮說，移民官建議張先生日後再到美國時，可以辦商務簽證，現在中美簽證十年有效，可多次往返，同樣可以滿足他的基本需求。<br />\n<br />\n雖然扣下綠卡，但此次海關仍然放張先生入境，以便辦理在美事宜，他可以請律師，向法官解釋為什麼不在美長居，因為移民官只能沒收綠卡，<strong>綠卡是否作廢卻不是海關說了算，只有法官才能做決定。</strong>"},{"pid":"4880ae0589e5f020b3f62af85099c1743d500b54","tid":102452,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:46:17.000Z","msg":"張先生昨天打電話給譚達榮，說他決定放棄綠卡，因為<strong>「取消永久居留權遞解程序」要上庭，靠律師據理力爭拿回綠卡，費時長久</strong>，期間本人不得出境美國，而他在大陸有很多生意，需要他回去打理。<br />\n<br />\n張先生的十年綠卡快到期，正準備更換新卡，已交了600美元換卡費，移民局通知他下月中旬「打指紋」，現在一切泡湯，他希望移民局能退回600美元。不過，譚達榮認為他申訴退款的機會為零，「因為出問題的是他自己，不是移民局。」譚達榮說這種情況下他能做的，就是把這名顧客原訂的回程機票截停，「否則他虧的更大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>綠卡持有者被盤查 並非個案</strong><br />\n<br />\n美加邊界以前通關作業一直寬鬆，很多華人就取道美加邊界，或循陸路方式出境，<span style=\"color: red;\">以為這樣可以不被美國移民官員發現</span>，但是自從911後，各個關卡的檢查已經嚴格許多。譚達榮說，他有好幾個顧客，都曾在美加邊界被攔下，沒收綠卡。<br />\n<br />\n他最近還碰到一例，一家四口從加拿大搭巴士返回美國，海關官員問家長有多少件行李，回答「五件」，官員馬上追問「在加拿大有多少天？」回答不出，官員當場把一家4口的綠卡全收走，給家長一張紙，限時到移民局回話。"},{"pid":"7d0c6a1c27e372a37726620eb7b50b3b9bfda3ea","tid":102452,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"譚達榮說，海關移民官員往往經驗老到，三言兩語後就可以判斷，旅客自稱到加拿大遊玩是假，繞道加拿大<span style=\"color: red;\">回中國是真</span>，否則，「四個人到加拿大玩幾天？需要五大件行李？」<br />\n<br />\n綠卡持有者在入關的時候被盤查，並非個案。<strong>有綠卡不等於往返美國暢通無阻</strong>，盤查的政策早已有之，只看海關的執法鬆嚴而已<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，「但是現在入關，他能查到十年綠卡，在美逗留不到三個月。」譚達榮說，這樣的個案，他還是第一次碰到，而且時間點正好在川普總統簽署移民禁令的期間，他因此要提醒持綠卡頻回大陸的民眾，「<strong>小心出國回不來</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。 <br />\n<br />\n責任編輯：艾倫<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/1/31/n8762457.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F17%2F1%2F31%2Fn8762457.htm&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7LzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=acdfd3c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/1/31/n8762457.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1f1913b7115c86be41e168fa802fe0a42f0aa163","tid":102452,"uid":73467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:53:36.000Z","msg":"返去蝗國，唔好累人累物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba6e7dfb958753617d64c6617e0e44e0496d547","tid":102452,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b9e2992005cc3d94ade5ee1553ffb34e777ee0","tid":102452,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:09:15.000Z","msg":"【大紀元2017年01月31日訊】<br />\n聽下算啦。"},{"pid":"89c8b235a015b0f02055026f2da4e1bd2c355d5b","tid":102452,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843168ea5cde3731e1a2dcb5ff00d9074444539a","tid":102452,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:33:00.000Z","msg":"綠卡唔係不嬲有居住時間要求既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c52cc1e63f4f42e09ec769b856998aafdfc02be","tid":102452,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:49:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d1c2fb2af7850675d50734d4a0f315aa3c5750","tid":102452,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:55:52.000Z","msg":"綠卡都可以俾人收<br />\n返香港拎定白卡都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1493efd1efc6f3c1dfc7e8696ec7d68fc35600","tid":102452,"uid":31762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T19:17:54.000Z","msg":"對於 alien 嚟講，美國機場櫃檯officer係有極大權力！幾十年嚟任何人揸 green card 返入美國境都有機會被認為冇誠意成為美國公民而被沒收！<br />\n<br />\n濕鳩記者唔撚識都可以打個電話問吓移民顧問吖唔該。"},{"pid":"a2da5b823cee29a12944627c37d3a213cf5cf6c7","tid":102452,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:08:52.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43eb29b824919b3d13c4e68cff08ac4a4510347a","tid":102452,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:44:25.000Z","msg":"華人？<br />\n支那狗就支那狗啦"},{"pid":"b7ee5c534c1a2f3ea35445fd887080333c964ed9","tid":102452,"uid":28287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:34:21.000Z","msg":"扺啦"},{"pid":"66ce81b1502f805bd66b4ba0f2adbb665059b43a","tid":102452,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:37:02.000Z","msg":"好耶"},{"pid":"8d096e2ac28a6bd215f169a8a6f24da252153f97","tid":102452,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:37:32.000Z","msg":"用美國角度睇真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3904b9c0c4f06bd80c06602f52a0ea05629194d","tid":102452,"uid":13628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:48:34.000Z","msg":"呢樣不嬲都係 一年冇住超過半年都嘈你 何況十年"},{"pid":"6d8fdcbe0509fbab0df7d45bea1f8d01b8e63ba9","tid":102452,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:01:50.000Z","msg":"佢自己違反規矩 根本唔關新總統事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d41b5d580e38959384d74f4ee91d6f2921ffa80","tid":102452,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:08:11.000Z","msg":"香港拎綜援人就長期係大陸，公屋用黎渡假同比d親戚黎玩個陣住"},{"pid":"68172b029a9a464fb8fc0eecdf0d4b55ec3fbbd3","tid":102452,"uid":28734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:20:41.000Z","msg":"不嬲綠卡都要坐移民監啦<br />\n佢自己冇可能唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}